Class InternalProfileCollector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.elasticsearch.search.profile.InternalProfileCollector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.lucene.search.Collector

    public class InternalProfileCollector
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.apache.lucene.search.Collector
    This class wraps a Lucene Collector and times the execution of: - setScorer() - collect() - doSetNextReader() - needsScores() InternalProfiler facilitates the linking of the the Collector graph
